      <tr><td>Circulation pump (near-silent)</td><td>$500 – $720</td><td>Full replacement</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Panel-ready hardware</td><td>Quoted individually</td><td>Custom-panel units</td></tr>
    </table>
    <p class="small">Related: <a href="/brands/ge-profile-dishwasher-repair/">GE Profile dishwasher repair</a> · <a href="/brands/ge-cafe-dishwasher-repair/">GE Café dishwasher repair</a> · <a href="/brands/ge-dishwasher-repair/">GE mainstream dishwasher repair</a> · <a href="/brands/ge-monogram-refrigerator-repair/">GE Monogram refrigerator repair</a>.</p>
  </div></section>

  <section class="section alt"><div class="wrap">
    <h2>Service areas, where our Monogram calls come from</h2>
    <div class="area-grid">
      <div><h4>Beverly Hills + Bel Air</h4><p><a href="/beverly-hills/">Beverly Hills</a> · Bel Air · Holmby Hills · Trousdale</p></div>
      <div><h4>Pacific Palisades + Brentwood</h4><p>Pacific Palisades · Brentwood · <a href="/santa-monica/">Santa Monica</a> · Rustic Canyon</p></div>
      <div><h4>Hollywood Hills + canyon</h4><p>Hollywood Hills · Laurel Canyon · Outpost Estates · Mount Olympus</p></div>
